Package game

Class Allosaur

java.lang.Object
edu.monash.fit2099.engine.Actor
game.Dinosaur
game.Allosaur
All Implemented Interfaces:
Capable, Printable, ActorInterface
public class Allosaur
extends Dinosaur
The class to create allosaurs the carnivorous dinosaur that finds and attacks stegosaurs and also will eat any form of meat, including the corpses, eggs and the meat meal kits.

  • Constructor Summary

    Constructors
    Constructor Description
    Allosaur​(java.lang.String name)
    The constructor to create Allosaur, they will be creates as babies, represented by 'a' and sets a random gender using the Dinosaur classes constructor and a health of 10.
    Allosaur​(java.lang.String name, java.lang.String gender)
    The admin constructor for the Allosaur, it will create baby Allosaur and the same things of the 1 parameter constructor but will also let the user set the gender of the Allosaur without it being random.
